  <brief_title>Comparison of Doubled Quadrupled Versus Quadrupled Allograft Tissue Constructs for Anterior Cruciate Ligament (ACL) Reconstruction</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective Randomized Comparison of Doubled Versus Quadrupled Allogenic Tissue Constructs for Anterior Cruciate Ligament Reconstruction</official_title>
