  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare two different soft tissue allografts, double bundle
      tibialis anterior allograft or quadruple bundle hamstring allograft, used in repairing a torn
      anterior cruciate ligament (ACL) of the knee.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
